| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1827 — Recovery Inhibition (clop)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 4fc146c6-7e1f-5a77-ab55-db0fbdca0b83"
